    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350400/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.poster.avif?t=1687403874\" width=591 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350400/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.webm?t=1687403874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>This is the story of a pig, who lived happily on his farm, food, mud and sleep were never lacking, until one day something changed.<br></li><li>So this pig decided that he did not want to be one more, that he did not want his life to be just food for others.<br></li><li>This Pig decides to take the law into his own hands to free himself from his oppression and his peers.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350400/extras/05d04b1d9117e35608a5f16ba3049c51.poster.avif?t=1687403874\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350400/extras/05d04b1d9117e35608a5f16ba3049c51.webm?t=1687403874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350400/extras/05d04b1d9117e35608a5f16ba3049c51.mp4?t=1687403874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This is the scoop on <strong>PIGNATOR</strong>, an action-packed First Person game, with a visual style that places us before a game that is inspired by the aesthetics and gameplay of old FPS games.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350400/extras/495a195bcfec115d582cd09bca34627e.webp?t=1687403874\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350400/extras/495a195bcfec115d582cd09bca34627e.poster.avif?t=1687403874\" class=\"bb_img\" width=302 height=55 /></picture></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Visual style of CRT Monitors<br></li><li>Pixel Art Graphics with 3D Environments<br></li><li>Hard Mode for more Hardcore players<br></li><li>Keyboard and mouse controls<br></li><li>Controller Compatibility<br></li><li>Wide screen resolution support<br></li><li>Native 60 FPS support<br></li><li>Multiplayer and local PVP<br></li><li>Horde mode</li></ul>",
